---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About"
  description="Learn about Joshuacord's mission, history, and the biblical story behind our name — standing with persecuted Christians worldwide."
>

  <!-- PAGE HERO -->
  <section class="relative bg-dark py-28 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-20">
      <img
        src="https://joshuacord.org/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/sadasdf-27-scaled.jpg"
        alt=""
        class="w-full h-full object-cover"
      />
    </div>
    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <p class="text-clay text-sm font-medium tracking-[0.2em] uppercase mb-4">Who We Are</p>
      <h1 class="font-display text-5xl sm:text-6xl text-white mb-5">About Joshuacord</h1>
      <div class="w-12 h-0.5 bg-brand mx-auto mb-6"></div>
      <p class="text-white/65 text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        A 501(c)(3) nonprofit bringing prayer, practical aid, and a voice of hope
        to Christians suffering for their faith around the world.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- THE NAME -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-sand">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <p class="text-brand text-sm font-medium tracking-[0.2em] uppercase">The Scarlet Cord</p>
          <h2 class="font-display text-4xl text-dark">The Story Behind the Name</h2>
          <div class="w-12 h-0.5 bg-brand"></div>
          <p class="text-dark/70 leading-relaxed">
            The name Joshuacord comes from the biblical account found in the book of Joshua.
            When Israelite spies entered Jericho, a woman named Rahab hid them at great personal
            risk. In return, the spies promised to spare her and her family — and their sign would
            be a scarlet cord hung in her window.
          </p>
          <p class="text-dark/70 leading-relaxed">
            That scarlet cord is a symbol of <strong class="text-dark">courage</strong>,
            <strong class="text-dark">faith</strong>, and <strong class="text-dark">kindness</strong>
            in the face of impossible odds. Rahab's story does not end there — she became the
            ancestor of King David, and through David, the ancestor of Jesus Christ himself.
          </p>
          <p class="text-dark/70 leading-relaxed">
            Like Rahab's cord, Joshuacord exists to mark those who would otherwise be forgotten —
            to say that the world sees them, that God has not abandoned them, and that they are
            <em>persecuted but not forgotten.</em>
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="relative">
          <img
            src="https://joshuacord.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/IRAQI-Children-Refugees-due-to-ISIL.jpg"
            alt="Children affected by persecution"
            class="w-full h-96 object-cover"
          />
          <div class="absolute -top-4 -left-4 w-24 h-24 border-4 border-clay -z-10"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- MISSION -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-sand-dark">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <p class="text-brand text-sm font-medium tracking-[0.2em] uppercase mb-3">Our Purpose</p>
      <h2 class="font-display text-4xl text-dark mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
      <div class="w-12 h-0.5 bg-brand mx-auto mb-10"></div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 text-left mt-4">
        <div class="bg-sand p-8 border-t-4 border-brand">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-brand/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-display text-xl text-dark mb-3">Prayer</h3>
          <p class="text-dark/65 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            We lift persecuted believers before God and mobilize the global church
            to intercede on their behalf. Prayer is not a last resort — it is our first response.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-sand p-8 border-t-4 border-brand">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-brand/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-display text-xl text-dark mb-3">Practical Aid</h3>
          <p class="text-dark/65 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Persecution often means job loss, displacement, and an inability to provide for families.
            We work to deliver tangible help to those in need.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-sand p-8 border-t-4 border-brand">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-brand/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M11 5.882V19.24a1.76 1.76 0 01-3.417.592l-2.147-6.15M18 13a3 3 0 100-6M5.436 13.683A4.001 4.001 0 017 6h1.832c4.1 0 7.625-1.234 9.168-3v14c-1.543-1.766-5.067-3-9.168-3H7a3.988 3.988 0 01-1.564-.317z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-display text-xl text-dark mb-3">Advocacy</h3>
          <p class="text-dark/65 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Through documentary films, public awareness campaigns, and direct outreach,
            we give a voice to those whose voices have been silenced.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SCRIPTURE -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-brand">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <blockquote>
        <p class="font-display text-2xl sm:text-3xl text-white italic leading-relaxed mb-6">
          "Have I not commanded you? Be strong and courageous.
          Do not be afraid; do not be discouraged, for the Lord your God
          will be with you wherever you go."
        </p>
        <cite class="text-white/70 text-sm font-medium not-italic tracking-wide uppercase">
          Joshua 1:9
        </cite>
      </blockquote>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FREEDOM 5K -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-sand">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div class="space-y-5">
          <p class="text-brand text-sm font-medium tracking-[0.2em] uppercase">Annual Event</p>
          <h2 class="font-display text-3xl text-dark">Joshua 1:9 Freedom 5K</h2>
          <div class="w-12 h-0.5 bg-brand"></div>
          <p class="text-dark/70 leading-relaxed">
            Each year, Joshuacord hosts the Joshua 1:9 Freedom 5K run to raise awareness
            and funds for persecuted Christians worldwide. Participants run in solidarity
            with believers who cannot freely worship, gather, or even speak the name of Christ.
          </p>
          <p class="text-dark/70 leading-relaxed">
            Every step is a declaration: the church is not silent, and our brothers and sisters
            around the world are not forgotten.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-sand-dark border border-clay/30 p-10 text-center">
          <p class="font-display text-6xl text-brand mb-2">5K</p>
          <p class="text-dark/60 text-sm uppercase tracking-wide">Annual Freedom Run</p>
          <div class="mt-6 pt-6 border-t border-clay/30">
            <p class="text-dark/70 text-sm">
              Contact us to learn about upcoming events or to host a Freedom 5K
              in your community.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CONTACT -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-dark" id="contact">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-14">
        <p class="text-clay text-sm font-medium tracking-[0.2em] uppercase mb-3">Get In Touch</p>
        <h2 class="font-display text-4xl text-white mb-4">Contact Us</h2>
        <div class="w-12 h-0.5 bg-brand mx-auto"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <!-- Contact info -->
        <div class="space-y-8">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-clay font-display text-xl mb-3">Mailing Address</h3>
            <address class="not-italic text-white/70 leading-relaxed text-sm">
              Joshuacord Inc.<br />
              3433 Lithia Pinecrest Road<br />
              Suite 120<br />
              Valrico, Florida 33596
            </address>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h3 class="text-clay font-display text-xl mb-3">Phone</h3>
            <a href="tel:+18134447905" class="text-white/70 hover:text-white transition-colors text-sm">
              (813) 444-7905
            </a>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h3 class="text-clay font-display text-xl mb-3">Follow Us</h3>
            <div class="flex gap-5 text-sm">
              <a
                href="https://www.facebook.com/joshuacord1.9"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="text-white/60 hover:text-clay transition-colors"
              >
                Facebook
              </a>
              <a
                href="https://twitter.com/joshua_cord"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="text-white/60 hover:text-clay transition-colors"
              >
                Twitter
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Contact form placeholder -->
        <div class="bg-sand/5 border border-sand/10 p-8">
          <h3 class="text-white font-display text-xl mb-6">Send a Message</h3>
          <form class="space-y-4">
            <div>
              <label class="block text-white/60 text-xs uppercase tracking-wide mb-2">Name</label>
              <input
                type="text"
                placeholder="Your name"
                class="w-full bg-sand/10 border border-sand/20 text-white placeholder-white/30 px-4 py-3 text-sm focus:outline-none focus:border-clay"
              />
            </div>
            <div>
              <label class="block text-white/60 text-xs uppercase tracking-wide mb-2">Email</label>
              <input
                type="email"
                placeholder="your@email.com"
                class="w-full bg-sand/10 border border-sand/20 text-white placeholder-white/30 px-4 py-3 text-sm focus:outline-none focus:border-clay"
              />
            </div>
            <div>
              <label class="block text-white/60 text-xs uppercase tracking-wide mb-2">Message</label>
              <textarea
                rows="4"
                placeholder="How can we help?"
                class="w-full bg-sand/10 border border-sand/20 text-white placeholder-white/30 px-4 py-3 text-sm focus:outline-none focus:border-clay resize-none"
              ></textarea>
            </div>
            <button
              type="submit"
              class="w-full bg-brand hover:bg-brand-dark text-white py-3 text-sm font-medium tracking-wide transition-colors"
            >
              Send Message
            </button>
          </form>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
